# 3D Web Workflows — vault policy

## Single sources (no duplicates)

| What | Canonical path |
|------|----------------|
| **Asset vault** | `D:\Hermes\assets\3d-web-workflows\` |
| **Agent hub doc** | `.cursor/docs/3D-WEB-WORKFLOWS.md` (from `sync:docs`) |
| **3d-scroll-website skill** | `.cursor/skills/3d-scroll-website/` (from `npm run sync:skills`) |
| **Taste catalog** | `.cursor/docs/3D-WEBSITE-TASTE-CATALOG.md` |

## Never

- Copy the vault into `.cursor/3d-web-workflows/` inside a project repo
- Store duplicate skill packs or `TOOLS-REFERENCE.md` in the vault
- Edit taste catalog in the vault — edit shared docs, then `npm run sync:docs -- -Write`

## Before scroll/3D builds

1. Read `.cursor/docs/3D-WEB-WORKFLOWS.md` + `.cursor/docs/3D-DEV-SETUP.md`
2. Run `npm run workflows:3d:status` + `npm run scroll:motion:status`
3. Trigger: `.cursor/prompts/Build-3D-Website.md`
4. Polish pass: **Design-Engineer** skill (screenshot rubric)
5. Quality gate: **cinematic-scroll-skill** `npm run doctor` in vault (≥ 80) — see Build-3D-Website Step 4
